NOTE: DECA Submodule Location
=============================

This directory (external/) is where the DECA Git submodule should be initialized.

To set up DECA:
  git submodule add https://github.com/yfeng95/DECA.git external/DECA
  git submodule update --init --recursive

After initialization, external/DECA/ will contain the full DECA repository.
The external/DECA/ directory is tracked as a submodule in .gitmodules,
NOT as regular files in this repository.
